          "en": "By this chain of transmission, from Ibrahim b. Muhammad al-Thaqafi. He said: Isma'il b. Aban al-Azdi informed us. He said: Abdullah b. Khirash al-Shaybani narrated to us from al-Awwam b. Hawshab from al-Taymi. He said: I visited A'isha, and she narrated to us that she saw the Messenger of Allah (may Allah bless him and his family)",
